title: Mrs Karen Smith
text: Taxi box came to the rescue after another company let us down. We had a tight schedule but taxi box was able to deliver on time and store our goods for the duration of the renovation. It was easy to organise for the return and the items came back in perfect order. Thanks for a great service. Happy to recommend you
